mysql解锁
(1)eappmysql -ueltedbm -peLTE@com234
(2)mysql> update mysql.user set Grant_priv='Y' where User='eltedbm';
(3)vi /etc/eapp3307/my.cnf 用#号注释掉127.0.0.1这一行
(4)service eappmysql restart

(5)eappmysql -ueltedbm -peLTE@com234
(6)mysql> grant all privileges on *.* to odb_user identified by 'eLTE@com123' with grant option;
(6)mysql> flush privileges;

MYSQL 解锁再发一次，大家记录一下，不要太依赖工具了哦。








4.0 解库方法
eappmysql 改为  mysql

3307 改为3306

etc/eapp3307/ 改为 /etc









mysql -ueltedbm -peLTE@com234
update mysql.user set Grant_priv='Y' where User='eltedbm';
vi /etc/my.cnf
service mysql restart
